    "Challenges and opportunitiesBased on the preceding analysis of deep learning-based software refactoring, we present here a list of potential challenges and opportunities for future research in deep learning-based software refactorings.",
    "Challenges• Large-scale high-quality dataset.",
    "It remains challenging to collect large-scale and high-quality refactoring data to train deep learning models.",
    "Although generating refactorings to be automatically reversed as suggested by Liu et al. [216] should result in large-scale refactoring data, the quality and representativeness are in question.",
    "In contrast, discovering refactoring histories in open-source applications may result in high-quality real-world refactoring data, such data are often small and lack diversity.• Generalization across different paradigms."
